Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛搞到兩張\N{\fs20}Hey, I just got us 2 tickets
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.69,0:00:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布拉德皮特新電影首映式的票\N{\fs20}to the premiere of the new Brad pitt movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.78,0:00:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikki\N{\fs20}Nikki...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.41,0:00:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候會有記者 會有攝影師\N{\fs20}There'll be reporters there. There'll be photographers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們會看到咱倆在一起\N{\fs20}People will see us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.38,0:00:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢\N{\fs20}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.71,0:00:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以\N{\fs20}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是地下情\N{\fs20}We're having a secret relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天吶 你太不擅長這個了\N{\fs20}God, you suck at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我們老是一起出去\N{\fs20}We used to hang out all the time before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在我們上床以前\N{\fs20}Yeah, well, that was before we were sleeping together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.47,0:00:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們那時候 是朋友\N{\fs20}We were... Friends then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在我們上床了 就不是朋友了\N{\fs20}Oh, so now that we're sleeping together, we can't be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不和朋友上床 Nikki\N{\fs20}I don't have sex with my friends, Nikki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是禽獸\N{\fs20}I'm not an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是受夠一直偷偷摸摸的了\N{\fs20}I'm just tired of sneaking around all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜心 我們這是謹慎\N{\fs20}Sweetie, we're being cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這叫慎重 好嗎\N{\fs20}We're being prudent, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.14,0:00:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不一樣\N{\fs20}There's a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷摸摸\N{\fs20}Sneaking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 Nikki\N{\fs20}Come on, Nikki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.97,0:00:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在要走了\N{\fs20}All right, I'm gonna leave now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你\N{\fs20}so you, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五分鐘之后在市場的拐角處和我匯合\N{\fs20}Wait 5 minutes meet me at the market around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 Nikki 跟以前一樣 如果我拿著一個菠蘿 \N{\fs20}And, Nikki, as always, if I'm holding a pineapple,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會取消\N{\fs20}abort.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Paul 你為什么遲到\N{\fs20}Hey, Paul. Why are you late?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.02,0:01:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這顯得一天不那么漫長\N{\fs20}I... It makes the day seem shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 上 好\N{\fs20}Go-o-o-ood morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike Nikki每天都遲到\N{\fs20}Mike, Nikki's late every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從來不為難她\N{\fs20}You never get on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你操心 Paul\N{\fs20}Oh, don't you worry, Paul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他今天一早就"調教"過我了\N{\fs20}He got on me earlier this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:02:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次 我很樂意見識一下\N{\fs20}Well, next time, Mike, I'd like to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎么的 我覺得再也沒心情了\N{\fs20}Somehow, I think that might ruin it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從體育商店買了什么\N{\fs20}Hey, what did you get at the sports depot?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我男朋友買了一根跳繩\N{\fs20}Just a jump rope for this guy I'm seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個正在訓練的運動員\N{\fs20}He's an athlete, and he's in training.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厄\N{\fs20}Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,備戰超級花式跳繩錦標賽嗎\N{\fs20}Big double Dutch tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikki 你桌上是我的鋼筆嗎\N{\fs20}Nikki, is that my... my pen on your desk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然穿了我的襯衫\N{\fs20}You're wearing my shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣 沒人會注意的\N{\fs20}So what? No one's gonna notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面繡著我的名字\N{\fs20}It's monogrammed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikki 我找到你想要的文件了\N{\fs20}Nikki, I found that file you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你捂住你的胸干嘛\N{\fs20}Why are you holding your breast?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.26,0:02:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早些 它們中有一個想逃跑\N{\fs20}Earlier, one of them tried to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有才\N{\fs20}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.11,0:02:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike 市長上<新聞熱議間>的提要\N{\fs20}Ok, Mike, I'm done with the mayor's notes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經寫好了\N{\fs20}for his appearance on politically incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.11,0:02:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}一檔真實存在的談話節目 本集中由主持人Bill Maher真人客串
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 James\N{\fs20}Great, James.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政治要求知己知彼\N{\fs20}You see, politics is all about preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出其不意是你最大的敵人\N{\fs20}Surprise is your worst enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何人 任何人 能讓Mike Flaherty吃驚\N{\fs20}And nobody, I mean nobody, surprises Mike Flaherty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊\N{\fs20}Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:02:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fs20}What?
