Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊\N{\fs20}Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了陳年的面包\N{\fs20}So, with day-old rolls,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些變硬的花生醬\N{\fs20}some dehydrated peanut paste
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上從餐館偷來的果凍\N{\fs20}and some stolen jelly packets from the diner,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我能給自己來一頓\N{\fs20}I figure I can give myself a nourishing lunch
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天8分錢的營養午餐\N{\fs20}for about 8 cents a day.
