Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我祖母給我做的\N{\fs20}My grandmother makes these for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人上癮\N{\fs20}They are so addictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才會上癮 你知道為什么嗎\N{\fs20}Addictive for you. You know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是個女人\N{\fs20}'Cause you're a woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你沒有定力\N{\fs20}and you're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗嘗\N{\fs20}Here.
