Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們什么時候和市長談談\N{\fs20}So, Mike, when are we gonna talk to the mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會 我現在有點不舒服\N{\fs20}Uh, later. I don't feel so good right now.
