Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥們 你真的應該去檢查下你的喉嚨\N{\fs20}Boy, you really oughta have someone take a look at that throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么\N{\fs20}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想讓別人看見我穿你的襯衫 那我就脫咯\N{\fs20}You didn't want people to see me in your shirt, so I took it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikki\N{\fs20}Nikki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在抗議 Mike\N{\fs20}I'm protesting, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想告訴大家咱倆的事\N{\fs20}I wanna tell people about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道會有點棘手\N{\fs20}I know it's gonna be awkward,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你知道嗎 我不在乎\N{\fs20}but you know what? I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不怕呢 我希望每個人都知道\N{\fs20}I'm not scared. I want everyone to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 Mike\N{\fs20}Hey, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 你就是嘴上說說\N{\fs20}Oh, you're all talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我跟你們解釋一下\N{\fs20}Let me explain something to ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙失去意識九個小時了\N{\fs20}The dude was out cold for 9 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 技術上來說 那不叫倒地\N{\fs20}Now, technically, that ain't no knockout.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫昏迷\N{\fs20}That's a coma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看這是誰啊 哪位猛男\N{\fs20}Hey, what are you, some kind of tough guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是崇拜者們想要看好戲 我必須效勞\N{\fs20}Oh, please. When the minions demand a show, I must oblige.
