Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜歡嗎\N{\fs20}You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carter 你不能在體育館里給我送禮物\N{\fs20}Carter, you can't bring me gifts at the gym.
